title: Ghana not underrating 104th ranked Canada ahead of friendly in Washington
text:
15:10 CET Ghana not underrating 104th ranked Canada ahead of friendly in Washington - www.ghanasoccernet.com Ghana preparing for the friendly in Washington 
George Afriyie insists the Black Stars will not underrate Canada in Tuesday's international friendly despite they not being known as a big football nation. 
The Black Stars will be taking on the Canadians in an international friendly in Washington. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
